[[File:ChampagneCorksLarge.jpg|thumb]]
'''軟木塞'''指的是用含有[[軟木脂|軟木脂]]而不滲水、柔軟而有浮力的木質製成的木塞。常用作[[葡萄酒|葡萄酒]]瓶塞，而選材主要是[[西班牙栓皮櫟|西班牙栓皮櫟]]。[[葡萄牙|葡萄牙]]的牧場（Dehesa）每年出產全球一半的軟木塞，而該國的{{tsl|en|Corticeira Amorim||Corticeira Amorim}}則是全球最大的軟木塞生產商。<ref>J. L. CALHEIROS E MENESES, President, Junta Nacional da Cortiça, Portugal. [http://www.uwec.edu/Geography/Ivogeler/Travel/Portugal/cork-article2.htm "The cork industry in Portugal"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.uwec.edu/Geography/Ivogeler/Travel/Portugal/cork-article2.htm |date=20120112090704 }}</ref>[[羅伯特·胡克|羅伯特·胡克]]正是經由對軟木塞的顯微觀察而發展出了[[細胞|細胞]]的概念。<ref name="urlRobert Hooke">{{cite web |url=http://www.ucmp.berkeley.edu/history/hooke.html |title=Robert Hooke |work= |accessdate=2010-11-03 |archive-date=2009-02-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090204111047/http://ucmp.berkeley.edu/history/hooke.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

==工業化==
[[File:1-Arraiolos-0050.jpg|thumb]]的樹皮]]
葡萄牙不僅是世界上最大的軟木塞生產國，全球50%以上的軟木塞用樹也都種植於葡萄牙和西班牙。軟木塞工業普遍被認為是環保<ref>Skidmore, Sarah, ''USA Today'' (August 26, 2007). [http://www.usatoday.com/money/industries/food/2007-08-26-cork-debate_N.htm "Stopper pulled on cork debate"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.usatoday.com/money/industries/food/2007-08-26-cork-debate_N.htm |date=20100712230244 }}</ref>而可持續的。因為即使需要砍伐樹木，一般也並不會伐掉整個樹林，而未被砍伐的樹還可以再次生長出樹皮來。用來製作軟木塞的西班牙栓皮櫟還是防止[[沙漠化|沙漠化]]的重要樹種之一，它還給許多生物提供了棲息之所。<ref>Henley, Paul, BBC.com (September 18, 2008)[http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/europe/7623912.stm "Urging vintners to put a cork in it"] {{Wayback|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/europe/7623912.stm |date=20210427080041 }}</ref>

{{tsl|en|Corticeira Amorim||Corticeira Amorim}}的[[碳足印|碳足跡]]研究顯示相對其他葡萄酒的[[代替用酒瓶蓋和瓶塞|代替用酒瓶蓋和瓶塞]]來說，軟木塞是最環保的選擇。<ref>[[PricewaterhouseCoopers|PricewaterhouseCoopers]]/ECOBILAN (October 2008). [http://www.corkfacts.com/pdffiles/Amorim_LCA_Final_Report.pdf Analysis of the life cycle of Cork, Aluminium and Plastic Wine Closures] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090913143609/http://www.corkfacts.com/pdffiles/Amorim_LCA_Final_Report.pdf |date=2009-09-13 }}.</ref>研究顯示每生產一個塑膠酒瓶蓋所排放的二氧化碳是軟木塞十倍，而鋁製酒瓶蓋更是達到二十六倍之多。

